repo_description: Free, open source, personal budgeting app

schemas.name: schema.graphql
schemas.content:
# source: http://localhost:5000/graphql
# timestamp: Sat Jan 05 2019 16:26:25 GMT-0600 (Central Standard Time)

schema {
  query: YABAQueryRoot
  mutation: YABAMutationRoot
}

type Account {
  id: Int!
  name: String!
}

input AccountCreateInput {
  name: String!
}

"""
The `Date` scalar type represents a year, month and day in accordance with the
[ISO-8601](https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/ISO_8601) standard.
"""
scalar Date

"""
The `DateTime` scalar type represents a date and time. `DateTime` expects
timestamps to be formatted in accordance with the
[ISO-8601](https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/ISO_8601) standard.
"""
scalar DateTime

"""
The `DateTimeOffset` scalar type represents a date, time and offset from UTC.
`DateTimeOffset` expects timestamps to be formatted in accordance with the
[ISO-8601](https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/ISO_8601) standard.
"""
scalar DateTimeOffset

scalar Decimal

"""
The `Milliseconds` scalar type represents a period of time represented as the total number of milliseconds.
"""
scalar Milliseconds

"""
The `Seconds` scalar type represents a period of time represented as the total number of seconds.
"""
scalar Seconds

type YABAMutationRoot {
  createAccount(account: AccountCreateInput!): Account
}

type YABAQueryRoot {
  accounts: [Account]
}
